✅ Purpose

Flexible relay between ports, protocols (TCP ↔ TCP, TCP ↔ UDP)

⚙️ Command (Pivot → Internal)

socat TCP-LISTEN:4444,fork TCP:192.168.1.10:3389

🔍 Explanation
TCP-LISTEN:4444 → Open port 4444 on pivot
fork → Handle multiple connections
TCP:192.168.1.10:3389 → Forward to internal RDP
🎯 Access from Attacker

